data.name: Bootstrapper.HyperionUpdateInfo
data.value:
Roblox ne ab naya game client update jaaree kar diya hai, jisamen 64-bit support aur hyperion anticheat shaamil hai. ReShade iss update ke saath kaam nahin karta hai, islie ise aksham kar diya gaya hai aur Bloxstrap se hata diya gaya hai.
Aapke ReShade configuration files abhee bhee sahejee jaengee, aur aap unhen us folder ko kholkar pa sakate hain jahaan bloxstrap install kiya gaya hai, aur phir integrations folder mein ja sakte hain. Yadi aap chaahen, to inhen hata sakate hain.

data.name: Menu.FastFlagEditor.LargeConfig
data.value:
Aap ek bahut bada configuration import kar rahe hain. Aapako keval vahee configuration aayaat karana chaahie jinhen aap pooree tarah se samajhate hain. Ani logon dvaara banae gae configurations ko bina jaane paste NA KAREN. Yadi aap jaaree rakhate hain, to bahut sambhaavana hai ki apko bohot sankat honge.
Kya aap vaakee import karna chaahate hain?

data.value: Apko pata he aap kya kar rahe he?

data.name: Menu.FastFlagEditor.Warning.Text
data.value:
Fast Flag atyant shaktishaalee hote hain, kyonki unaka upayog keval Roblox engineers dvaara kiya jaata hai. Haalaanki ve bahut upayogee ho sakate hain, unhen manually roop se configure karane se sthirata aur kaaryakshamata ke saath gambheer samasyaen paida ho sakatee hain. Yadi aap anishchit hain ki aap kya kar rahe hain to editor ka upayog NA KAREN.
Isaka upayog any logon dvaara banaee gaee badee "flag lists" ko aayaat karane ke lie NA KAREN jo nishpadan ya is tarah ke sudhaar ka vaada karatee hain. Ve uparokt muddon ke adheen hain, aur ve aapake lie samasyaen paida karenge kyonki aapako is baat kee pooree jaanakaaree nahin hogee ki ve kya badal rahe hain. Yadi aap aisa karane vaale the, to VAAPAS JAEN.
